     <div class="arriba clearfix colelem shared_content" id="u125381-7" data-content-guid="u125381-7_content"><!-- content -->
      <p id="u125381-2">Alcohol/Drug Clinical Evaluation</p>
      <p id="u125381-4">(also known as DUI Clinical Evaluation)</p>
      <p id="u125381-5">&nbsp;</p>
     </div>
     <div class="clearfix colelem shared_content" id="pu125401-4" data-content-guid="pu125401-4_content"><!-- group -->
      <div class="arriba clearfix grpelem" id="u125401-4"><!-- content -->
       <p id="u125401-2">BEFORE</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arriba clearfix grpelem" id="u126975-4"><!-- content -->
       <p id="u126975-2">AFTER</p>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="clearfix colelem shared_content" id="pu126978" data-content-guid="pu126978_content"><!-- group -->
      <div class="clip_frame grpelem" id="u126978"><!-- image -->
       <img class="block temp_no_img_src" id="u126978_img" data-orig-src="images/before.png?crc=3926349490" alt="" width="206" height="310" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/>
      </div>
      <div class="clip_frame grpelem" id="u126988"><!-- image -->
       <img class="block temp_no_img_src" id="u126988_img" data-orig-src="images/after.png?crc=4125762812" alt="" width="230" height="310" src="images/blank.gif?crc=4208392903"/>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="arriba clearfix colelem shared_content" id="u125384-4" data-content-guid="u125384-4_content"><!-- content -->
      <p>ALFA is now offering State/DHR approved Drug and Alcohol Evaluations for court, drugs and/or possession.&nbsp; A DUI Clinical Evaluation is required for charges by the state for driving while under the influence (DUI) or a DUI charge that has been reduced to reckless driving. DUI Clinical Evaluations are regulated by the state of Georgia DUI Intervention Program for all persons charged with a DUI.</p>
     </div>
     <div class="clearfix colelem shared_content" id="pu127704" data-content-guid="pu127704_content"><!-- group -->
      <div class="browser_width grpelem shared_content" id="u127704-bw" data-content-guid="u127704-bw_content">
       <div id="u127704"><!-- column -->
        <div class="clearfix" id="u127704_align_to_page">
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127004-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Approved</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127007-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>DDS license, DBHDD and Court Approved. Evaluation report provided for court, probation and/or attorney.</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127016-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Offered Daily</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127019-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Call us to schedule your evaluation.&nbsp; Most evaluations take approximately 20-30 minutes to complete.</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127022-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Convenient Locations</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127025-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Alfa has 7 locations at your service. Short drive from anywhere.</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127028-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Easy to Schedule</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127031-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Quick and easy to register via phone or in-person.</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127037-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>Lowest Fee by Law</p>
         </div>
         <div class="arriba clearfix colelem" id="u127034-4"><!-- content -->
          <p>$95 - $150.&nbsp; Fee is based on 1st offense or multiple offenses.</p>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grpelem shared_content" id="u127707" data-mu-ie-matrix="progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Matrix(M11=0.7071,M12=0.7071,M21=-0.7071,M22=0.7071,SizingMethod='auto expand')" data-mu-ie-matrix-dx="-9" data-mu-ie-matrix-dy="-9" data-content-guid="u127707_content"><!-- simple frame --></div>
      <div class="grpelem" id="u127713" data-mu-ie-matrix="progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.Matrix(M11=0.7071,M12=0.7071,M21=-0.7071,M22=0.7071,SizingMethod='auto expand')" data-mu-ie-matrix-dx="-9" data-mu-ie-matrix-dy="-9"><!-- simple frame --></div>
